The '''Torine''' were [[Near-Human]]s indigenous to [[Torina]]. They were set on the cause of preserving the environment of their [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]]. They also ran a thriving tourism industry on their world, including [[Hotel/Legends|hotels]], [[Cantina|bars]], and [[casino]]s, and were renowned for their manufacture of electronics as well. Despite, or perhaps because of, their prosperity, they were fearful of losing what they had to the oppression of the [[Galactic Empire]]. Accordingly, the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] attempted to court the Torines to their favor.<ref name="POTG3">''[[Planets of the Galaxy, Volume Three]]''</ref>

